COMMON API PATTERNS

AUTH HEADER
```
-H "Authorization: Bearer $CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN"
-H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

LIST ZONES
```bash
curl -s "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/zones?account.id=$ACCOUNT_ID" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN"
```

LIST DNS RECORDS
```bash
curl -s "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/zones/$ZONE_ID/dns_records" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN"
```

CREATE A RECORD (PROXIED)
```bash
curl -s -X POST "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/zones/$ZONE_ID/dns_records" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  --data '{"type":"A","name":"example.com","content":"89.167.12.82","ttl":1,"proxied":true}'
```

CREATE CNAME (www â†’ root)
```bash
curl -s -X POST "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/zones/$ZONE_ID/dns_records" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  --data '{"type":"CNAME","name":"www","content":"example.com","ttl":1,"proxied":true}'
```

DELETE DNS RECORD
```bash
curl -s -X DELETE "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/zones/$ZONE_ID/dns_records/$RECORD_ID" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN"
```

UPDATE DNS RECORD
```bash
curl -s -X PUT "https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/zones/$ZONE_ID/dns_records/$RECORD_ID" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  --data '{"type":"A","name":"example.com","content":"89.167.12.82","ttl":1,"proxied":true}'
```

NEW DOMAIN SETUP WORKFLOW

1. GET ZONE ID: Query `/zones?name=domain.com`
2. CREATE DNS RECORDS:
   - A record for root (`domain.com`) â†’ `89.167.12.82` (proxied)
   - CNAME for `www` â†’ `domain.com` (proxied)
3. UPDATE COOLIFY DB:
   - `docker exec coolify-db psql -U coolify -c "UPDATE applications SET fqdn = 'https://existing.com,https://newdomain.com,https://www.newdomain.com' WHERE uuid = '...'"`
   - Clear custom_labels: `UPDATE applications SET custom_labels = NULL WHERE uuid = '...'`
4. TRIGGER REDeploy: `POST /api/v1/applications/{uuid}/restart`
5. VERIFY: `curl -sI https://newdomain.com` returns 200

NOTES
- Cloudflare proxy (orange cloud) = traffic through CF edge, hides server IP, DDoS protection
- TTL=1 = automatic when proxied
- SSL mode = "Full (strict)" (Traefik provides valid Let's Encrypt certs)
- Server IP: `89.167.12.82` (Hetzner CX33)
